2009-06-30 18:23 +0000 [r204469]  Tilghman Lesher <tlesher@digium.com>

	* main/say.c, UPGRADE.txt: "tw" is the language specification for
	  Twi (from Ghana) not Taiwanese. (closes issue #15346) Reported
