	  voicemail, and fixed several other bugs while I'm in the area.
	  (closes issue #11615) Reported by: jamessan Patches:
	  20071226__bug11615__2.diff.txt uploaded by Corydon76 (license 14)
	  Tested by: Corydon76, jamessan

