	  Jul 2007) | 8 lines (closes issue #10075) Reported by: apsaras
	  Patches submitted by: Corydon76 Tested by: apsaras Fix a problem
	  with MSSQL 2005 by explicitly stating that '\' is being used as
	  an escape character. ........

