	  from https://origsvn.digium.com/svn/asterisk/branches/1.2
	  ........ r62737 | murf | 2007-05-02 14:10:32 -0600 (Wed, 02 May
	  2007) | 1 line Some tweaks to satisfy CDR bug 8796, where being
	  in 'h' extension louses up the dst field ........

