2007-04-26 16:33 +0000 [r61959-62038]  Joshua Colp <jcolp@digium.com>

	* /, channels/chan_iax2.c: Merged revisions 62037 via svnmerge from
	  https://origsvn.digium.com/svn/asterisk/branches/1.2 ........
